                        "id": "18106023739710651",
                        "text": "Tokyo\u2019s lucky cat\u2013themed vinyl jazz bar \ud83d\udc31\ud83c\udfb6\n\nHidden upstairs in Shinjuku, this spot has been run by a husband-and-wife team since 1979. Inside, there are 2,500+ maneki-neko (\u62db\u8ca1\u8c93) everywhere\u2014lining the walls, stacked in cabinets, basically watching you drink.\n\nIt\u2019s all vinyl jazz, picked by the owner Miyazaki-san, with signed album sleeves on the walls from his time in New York back in the \u201970s. Super cozy, a little quirky, and very Tokyo.\n\nSnacks are around \u00a5350\u2013\u00a5850 (~$2\u20136 USD) and drinks are around \u00a5700 ($5 USD).\n\ud83d\udccdJazz Bar Samurai Jazz Bar \u30b5\u30e0\u30e9\u30a4\n\ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f Japan, \u3012160-0022 Tokyo, Shinjuku City, Shinjuku, 3 Chome\u221235\u22125 \u5b88\u30d3\u30eb 5F\n.\n#vinyl #vinylbar #jazzbar #tokyo #japan #visittokyo #tokyotravel #tokyotrip #visitjapan #tokyobar"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
